    "ailments_description": "The most common ailments you can heal with Sarcochilus viridiflorus are fever, which is effectively reduced by its antipyretic properties. Inflammation is another condition that is alleviated by this plant due to its anti-inflammatory compounds. Sarcochilus viridiflorus is also used to treat digestive issues such as diarrhea and dysentery, thanks to its anthelmintic and purgative properties. Furthermore, it has been shown to possess antimicrobial properties, making it effective against bacterial and fungal infections. Additionally, Sarcochilus viridiflorus has been used to treat respiratory issues like bronchitis and asthma due to its expectorant and bronchodilator properties.",
